{"id": "1200856771875586048", "channel_id": "1200856771875586048", "type": 0, "author_id": "841362944934543400", "author_name": "2kageyama4", "author_bot": false, "content": "前期急着推进度跳了剧情，现在想重新看但是实在是不想再重新打个关卡了，打牌真的很耗时间......cg做成相册之类的功能也会方便查看截图", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T17:36:05.255000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200856771875586048", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」希望能出一个剧情模式/cg相册之类的功能，还有能在游戏里查看角色全身立绘的地方.....", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1200747452114939925", "channel_id": "1200747452114939925", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "如图，大致说明了我作为均养玩家最开始的想法和如今的困境，希望官方尽早改善游戏体验。", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T10:21:41.393000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1200747452563726356", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 653862, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1200747452114939925/1200747452563726356/image.png?ex=69cc48f5&is=69caf775&hm=b85c85ba1d1b89c76f49ca24bd218e98b095adfd3a55280bb26892763dc8d642&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200747452114939925", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」均衡养成玩家的起源与窘境", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1181168183319736412"]}
{"id": "1200794375924482120", "channel_id": "1200794375924482120", "type": 0, "author_id": "1157675500014153860", "author_name": "youluo0436", "author_bot": false, "content": "這邊有以下幾個建議希望官方可以考慮並實裝進入遊戲中。\n\n1.）劇情模式\n\n希望會出，不然每一次要重溫劇情都要再打一遍關卡很麻煩……\n\n2.）自選UP\n\n可以考慮實裝進常駐池裡，讓各位守密人自選命輪和角色。\n\n如果選擇該角色或該命輪的話那麼這個角色或命輪的概率就會提高，如果抽到了不是自己選的命輪或角色的話，那麼下一次抽到時就必定是自己選的命輪或角色\n\n3.）角色時裝\n\n希望可以出角色們的其他服裝……，也想看他們穿其他衣服的樣子！（算是我個人的私心……）\n\n也希望多出一點SR角色！", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T13:28:08.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200794375924482120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」忘卻前夜 遊戲建議", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1200809335861821592", "channel_id": "1200794375924482120", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "第二條同意，很不理解官方的限時池過後三個月復刻，一年進普池，一年之後都不知道多少玩家退遊了，這個一年真的太搞笑了。還不如直接出角色dlc課金禮包來的痛快些。😅", "timestamp": "2024-01-27T14:27:35.628000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1200794375924482120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」忘卻前夜 遊戲建議", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
